Text: This torrent is a fake. In fact, I haven't seen a working keygen for Super Flexible File Synchronizer for years. After a couple of months SFFS starts complaining the evaluating period is over and the keygen doesn't help at all. SFFS needs a working crack! CORE can you hear me?
